question: What restaurant is available on the route to Studio Two Three, Richmond City, VA within a 150 kilometers radius from Historic Site: Presbyterian Meetinghouse, Williamsburg, VA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.691858 37.27148)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.473955 37.568535)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.691858 37.27148)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.691858 37.27148)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
